# ROS 2 (not ROS 1)

This project uses **ROS 2 Jazzy**. Use:

- `rclpy` (not `rospy`)
- `std_msgs/msg/String` (not `std_msgs/String`)
- `rclpy.Rate`, `rclpy.Node` (not rospy equivalents)
- DDS / `ROS_DOMAIN_ID` for discovery

Do not use ROS 1 patterns (rospy, roscore, catkin, rosrun, roslaunch XML).
